# Frontend Components Guide

## Pages
- `frontend/src/presentation/pages/` - Main page components
  - `Login.tsx` - Authentication page
  - `Dashboard.tsx` - Main application dashboard
  - `EmailEditor.tsx` - Rich text email editor

## Layout Components
- `frontend/src/presentation/components/` - Reusable layout components
  - `Sidebar.tsx` - Main navigation sidebar
  - `Header.tsx` - Application header
  - `Layout.tsx` - Main layout wrapper

## Theme Components
- `frontend/src/shared-theme/` - Theme and UI components
  - `theme.ts` - Theme configuration
  - `ColorModeIconDropdown.tsx` - Theme mode switcher
  - `LanguageSelect.tsx` - Language selector

## Context Providers
- `frontend/src/presentation/contexts/` - React context providers
  - `AuthContext.tsx` - Authentication state
  - `ThemeContext.tsx` - Theme state
  - `LanguageContext.tsx` - Internationalization state

## Services
- `frontend/src/services/` - API service classes
  - `AuthService.ts` - Authentication service
  - `EmailService.ts` - Email communication service
  - `WebSocketService.ts` - Real-time communication


